== Swedish ==
=== Etymology ===
Literally &ldquo;the war of the ants,&rdquo; or &ldquo;the battle of the ants.&rdquo;
=== Noun phrase ===
'''[[myrornas]] [[krig]]'''
# [[random|Random]], usually [[monochromatic]], [[video]] [[noise]] (typically caused by a [[white noise]] input signal to a [[television]], often due to lack of [[reception]]), in which the [[white]] [[ant]]s are fighting the [[black]] ants in an endless [[metaphorical]] [[battle]].
==== Synonyms ====
[[brus]], [[snö]]
==== Translations ====
English: [[static]], [[noise]], [[snow]]

